- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with improving the performance of a neural machine translation model. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is less likely but still possible as the paper mentions using bin-packing parallel batching technique to maximize CPU utilization, which could be relevant to computer vision tasks. 
- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is also less likely but possible as the paper deals with optimizing performance on Intel CPUs.
